<% @page_title = "Checkout" %>

<div class="home-test">

  <div class="top">
    <div class="inside">
      <div class="left">
        <h1>At-Home DNA Paternity Testing</h1>
        <p>
          The At-Home DNA Paternity Test Kit provides everything you need to test for paternity in the comfort and privacy of your home, with 99.9% accuracy.
        </p>

        <div class="pricing">
          <h4>Pricing:</h4>
          <p><b>$179</b> for 1 child, and 1 potential father</p>
          <p><b>$100</b> per additional recipient</p>
          <p><span>Price includes: testing kit, shipping, and results.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="right">
        <%= image_tag('test-kit-slide.png', class: 'img-responsive', alt: 'Get DNA Tested Today, home kit') %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="checkout">
    <div class="inside">
      <h4>At-Home DNA Paternity Test Kit </h4>
      <%= form_tag charges_path do %>
        <article>
          <% if flash[:error].present? %>
            <div id="error_explanation">
              <p><%= flash[:error] %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          <label class="amount">
            <h5>Pricing:</h5>
            <p><b>$179</b> for 1 Child and 1 Potential Father</p>
            <p><b>$100</b> for each additional Participant</p>
            <p><span>Price includes: testing kit, shipping, and results.</span></p>
          </label>
        </article>

        <script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
        data-key="<%= Rails.configuration.stripe[:publishable_key] %>"
        data-description="At Home DNA Test"
        data-amount="17900"
        data-zip-code="true"
        data-billing-address="true"
        data-shipping-address="true"
        data-locale="auto"></script>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="full-pg">
    <div class="inside">
      <h3>When you receive your Home Test Kit, follow these simple steps:</h3>

      <p><b>Step 1.</b> <span>Label Swab Envelopes:</span><br> The information must be filled out completely for test to be accurate.</p>

      <p><b>Step 2.</b> <span>Collect DNA Samples:</span><br> Simply rub the Sterile Polyester Tipped Applicators for 30 seconds inside the cheeks of the individuals being tested.</p>

      <p><b>Step 3.</b> <span>Place Applicator in Sample Envelope:</span><br> Remove the applicator from mouth and place it directly into the DNA Sample Envelope labeled for that tested person.</p>

      <p><b>Step 4.</b> <span>Mail DNA Samples:</span><br> Detach the Business Reply Envelope portion of the kit, then place all the collected parties' DNA Sample Envelopes inside.<br> Seal the envelope securely, and place in the mail. </p>

      <p>Once we receive and test the samples, we will contact you with the results.</p></p>
    </div>
  </div>



  <!-- <%= image_tag('baby.png', class: 'full-img', alt: 'Get DNA Tested Today, baby border image') %>  -->
</div>
